Interface DisplayRenderableProvider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Disposable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AircraftDotModel, AircraftInfoModel, BreadCrumbModel, HudModel, PredictionModel, SimpleDisplayRenderableProvider, TracksModel, VelocityModel, WorldMapModel

    public interface DisplayRenderableProvider
extends Disposable
    This interface represents any object which is able to provide Model gdxRenderableProviders to RenderLayers in the display.
